      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and serves as a dependable choice for anyone needing reliable transportation. While it remains mechanically sound and has been regularly serviced to ensure it runs well, the exterior shows clear signs of use, including several noticeable scratches, minor dings, and some paint fading on the hood. The interior is functional but shows visible wear on the seats and carpet consistent with its age. It is a solid, honest car for someone prioritizing utility over aesthetics.",
