    {
      "id": "sybil_10_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_10",
      "description": "Offered is a mechanically sound E46 M3 featuring the high-revving S54B32 inline-six engine equipped with individual throttle bodies and a 8,000 RPM redline. This example features a Getrag 6-speed manual transmission and a factory-spec limited-slip differential. Critical preventative maintenance has been addressed, including a comprehensive dual-VANOS overhaul and a reinforced rear subframe to ensure structural rigidity under lateral load. The suspension retains its factory-tuned damping characteristics with refreshed bushings for precise turn-in. While the aesthetic reflects honest use, the powertrain exhibits excellent compression and smooth power delivery throughout the powerband. A driver-focused machine with the mechanical pedigree to match.",
      "price": 33800.0,
      "reputation": 0.4,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 46
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_11_listing_3",
