      "description": "This vehicle has been meticulously cared for and presents beautifully in its original factory finish. While it shows the expected signs of light use typical for its age, the body remains straight and free of major blemishes. Inside, you\u2019ll find a smoke-free cabin with plush leather seating that has been conditioned regularly to maintain its integrity. Mechanically, this car is sound; I have stayed ahead of all scheduled maintenance, including recent oil changes and a fresh set of all-season tires. It drives smoothly, shifts effortlessly, and all electronic features\u2014from the responsive infotainment system to the climate control\u2014function exactly as they should. This is a reliable, high-quality example ready for its next owner to enjoy immediately without any hidden surprises.",
